acceptOwnership().details: The new owner accepts the ownership transfer.

params.extraRewarder: The extra rewarder of the farm.

claim(uint256[]).details: Claims the rewards from a list of farms.

params.pids: The pool IDs of the farms.

params.factory: The address of the rewarder factory.
params.futureFundingShare: The share of the rewards that will be sent to the future funding.
params.moe: The address of the MOE token.
params.teamShare: The share of the rewards that will be sent to the team.
params.treasuryShare: The share of the rewards that will be sent to the treasury.
params.veMoe: The address of the VeMOE contract.

params.amount: The amount of tokens to deposit.
params.pid: The pool ID of the farm.

emergencyWithdraw(uint256).details: Emergency withdraws tokens from a farm, without claiming any rewards.

params.pid: The pool ID of the farm.

getDeposit(uint256,address).details: Returns the deposit amount of an account on a farm.

params.account: The account to check for the deposit amount.
params.pid: The pool ID of the farm.

returns._0: The deposit amount of the account on the farm.

getExtraRewarder(uint256).details: Returns the extra rewarder of a farm.

params.pid: The pool ID of the farm.

returns._0: The extra rewarder of the farm.

getFutureFunding().details: Returns the address of the future funding vesting contract.

returns._0: The address of the future funding.

getFutureFundingShare().details: Returns the share of the rewards that will be sent to the future funding.

returns._0: The share of the rewards that will be sent to the future funding.

getLastUpdateTimestamp(uint256).details: Returns the last update timestamp of a farm.

params.pid: The pool ID of the farm.

returns._0: The last update timestamp of the farm.

getMoe().details: Returns the address of the MOE token.

returns._0: The address of the MOE token.

getMoePerSecondForPid(uint256).details: Returns the MOE per second for a given pool ID. If the pool ID is not in the top pool IDs, it will return 0. Else, it will return the MOE per second multiplied by the proportion of votes for this pool ID.

returns._0: The MOE per second for the pool ID.

getPendingRewards(address,uint256[]).details: Returns the pending rewards for a given account on a list of farms.

params.account: The account to check for pending rewards.
params.pids: The pool IDs of the farms.

returns.extraRewards: The extra rewards amounts from the extra rewarders.
returns.extraTokens: The extra tokens from the extra rewarders.
returns.moeRewards: The MOE rewards for the account on the farms.

getRewarderFactory().details: Returns the address of the rewarder factory.

returns._0: The address of the rewarder factory.

getTeam().details: Returns the address of the team vesting contract.

getTeamShare().details: Returns the share of the rewards that will be sent to the team.

returns._0: The share of the rewards that will be sent to the team.

getToken(uint256).details: Returns the token of a farm.

params.pid: The pool ID of the farm.

getTotalDeposit(uint256).details: Returns the total deposit amount of a farm.

params.pid: The pool ID of the farm.

returns._0: The total deposit amount of the farm.

getTreasury().details: Returns the address of the treasury.

getTreasuryShare().details: Returns the share of the rewards that will be sent to the treasury.

returns._0: The share of the rewards that will be sent to the treasury.

getVeMoe().details: Returns the address of the VeMOE contract.

returns._0: The address of the VeMOE contract.

params.futureFunding: The initial future funding vesting contract.
params.initialOwner: The initial owner of the contract.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

pendingOwner().details: Returns the address of the pending owner.

setExtraRewarder(uint256,address).details: Sets the extra rewarder of a farm.

params.extraRewarder: The new extra rewarder of the farm.
params.pid: The pool ID of the farm.

setFutureFunding(address).details: Sets the future funding vesting contract.

params.futureFunding: The new future funding vesting contract.

setMoePerSecond(uint96).details: Sets the MOE per second. It will update all the farms that are in the top pool IDs.

transferOwnership(address).details: Starts the ownership transfer of the contract to a new account. Replaces the pending transfer if there is one. Can only be called by the current owner.

updateAll(uint256[]).details: Updates all the farms in the pids list.

params.amount: The amount of tokens to withdraw.
params.pid: The pool ID of the farm.
